# InferTest — expected entailments
# Construct : owl:unionOf (class union)

@prefix : <http://example.org/infertest#> .
@prefix rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> .

### MyCar is a Car, and Vehicle is the union of Car and Truck -> MyCar must
### be typed Vehicle.
:UnionOf_MyCar rdf:type :UnionOf_Vehicle .
